 4 videos on a cd\\/dvd tracing their realistico-imaginary journey through 4 cities: a crime in Brest, a return to their roots in Comines-Komen (a Franco-Belgian city from their origins), a documentary on Paris and a dream in Boubek (imaginary town, half norman, half northern) on which they invited a native to set voice and text. True to their wacky minds, Trip to Trip is pop melodies, punk rage, a free spirit and 8bit sounds. An energetic voyage that will give you a taste for vacation...\",\"lang\":\"en\"}','{\"presentation\":\"Bleep bleep punks Ben and B\\u00e9n\\u00e9 are piling up demos recorded in their kitchen since 2003. For the release of their EP on the Parisian net-label Da ! Heard It Records, they decided this time to pack up mics, computers and gameboy in their car.\\nA few months later, this improvised move gave birth to Trip to Trip: 4 titles and 4 videos on a cd\\/dvd tracing their realistico-imaginary journey through 4 cities: a crime in Brest, a return to their roots in Comines-Komen (a Franco-Belgian city from their origins), a documentary on Paris and a dream in Boubek (imaginary town, half norman, half northern) on which they invited a native to set voice and text. True to their wacky minds, Trip to Trip is pop melodies, punk rage, a free spirit and 8bit sounds. An energetic voyage that will give you a taste for vacation...\",\"lang\":\"en\",\"release_id\":\"3\"}','release','3',1),(557,724,'release_translation','6','{\"id\":\"6\",\"release_id\":\"3\",\"presentation\":\"Les deux punks bleep bleep Ben et B\\u00e9n\\u00e9 accumulent les d\\u00e9mos enregistr\\u00e9es dans leur cuisine depuis 2003. Pour la sortie de leur EP sur le net-label parisien Da ! Heard It Records, ils ont d\\u00e9cid\\u00e9, cette fois,d\\u2019embarquer micros, ordinateurs et gameboy dans leur voiture.\\nQuelques mois plus tard, ce d\\u00e9m\\u00e9nagement improvis\\u00e9 donne naissance \\u00e0 Trip to Trip : 4 titres et 4 vid\\u00e9os sur un cd\\/dvd retra\\u00e7ant leur p\